{"tid":1741064,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「黎明行動」塞鐵藍絲、便衣真正最大敵人","createTime":"2019-11-20T07:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T14:32:18.000Z","uid":42093,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"64c9e85c16be093d76ca2b5c255980b479bde0c5","tid":1741064,"uid":42093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:27:28.000Z","msg":"大家睇到塞鐵既學生、手足俾人打，<br />\n但又面對成車藍絲無辦法幫手覺得好無力？<br />\n幫拖又唔係唔幫拖又唔係。<br />\n平時我地私了既最大敵人從來唔係狗，係左膠！<br />\n同樣道理，<br />\n其實佢地最大既敵人係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「藍和理非」、「藍左膠」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只要扮演番一個自私既藍絲就可以化解暴力。</span><br />\n<br />\n例子1：你地咪打交呀，一陣我要去做證人咪無工番！<br />\n例子2：咪打交呀，有人起左底工都無埋，唔好搞事啦！<br />\n例子3：喂，你一打就停車架啦，我趕時間架，手停口停！<br />\n例子4：喊，拉住D藍絲唔好俾佢打（女性限定）<br />\n<br />\n大家如果活用以上例子加以創作，手足被打既機會就低好多，<br />\n便衣防暴都俾你搞到亂晒。咁如果你大大個黃絲樣，就咪用呢招啦。"},{"pid":"14f2c386bb252b49b48feedfffefb16268c42809","tid":1741064,"uid":263261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:28:17.000Z","msg":"藍左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58315c0644e06f5bd29e9a16dd5db0e13af0ad7f","tid":1741064,"uid":42093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:29:51.000Z","msg":"推，藍左膠先可以停止暴力"},{"pid":"cc27e54711744040c90f20c7f11be18dc6d950df","tid":1741064,"uid":42093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:30:41.000Z","msg":"推到一車藍左膠"},{"pid":"d6111b538cfe74891bc2af40a54a401b3e785585","tid":1741064,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:31:34.000Z","msg":"便衣MMA 真係想炸裂佢老母，肥豬公"},{"pid":"badd44270f719a739be76a71be0792b0cfe2bd18","tid":1741064,"uid":42093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d6111b538cfe74891bc2af40a54a401b3e785585","tid":1741064,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike"